{"id":18765,"date":"2024-01-29T18:25:53","date_gmt":"2021-01-29T12:55:53","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=18765"},"modified":"2022-05-29T15:26:21","modified_gmt":"2022-05-29T09:56:21","slug":"hall-furniture-design-ideas","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/hall-interiors\/hall-furniture-design-ideas\/","title":{"rendered":"8 Hall Furniture Design Ideas For Your Home"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p><em>Skim through our latest collection of the best furniture designs for the hall that will convert your space into a zone of comfort and completeness. We\u2019re sure you\u2019ll love them!<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Your hall is the space where you spend a lot of time, be it alone or with family and friends. Make it count by transforming it into a more comfortable and elegant space. Choose hall furniture designs that reflect your personality and lifestyle and blend it in with the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/interior-design\/\">interior design<\/a> of the space \u2014 no matter what size it is.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Here are a few key rules that you should keep in mind to ensure that your furniture design for the hall is the right fit:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><li>The furniture pieces should be approachable, adaptable and shouldn\u2019t look odd. Place the chairs and sofas around a large window so that you can take full advantage of the sunlight and views<\/li><li>The kind of furniture you choose and how it\u2019s placed in the hall also determines its overall look and feel. If you want to create an informal vibe, go for an asymmetrical layout by incorporating a <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/sectional-sofa-design-ideas\/\">sectional sofa<\/a> and a few pouffes or bean bags for extra seating. If you want a formal and symmetrical space, pair a standard sofa set with a coffee table in the centre and a side table on either end<\/li><li>The height of your furniture design also needs to be optimised. Also, the number of dining chairs should roughly match the number of seating areas in the hall&nbsp;<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Here are our eight favourite furniture design ideas for the hall that will surely leave you in awe.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Hall Furniture Design That Creates A Nook<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This is an ideal representation of a modern hall furniture design. The yellow sofa and the grey armchairs provide sufficient and comfy seating space while the round tables complement the carpet, the lamps, wooden flooring and the light walls.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/29182056\/hall-furniture-design-with-sofa-set.jpg\" alt=\"White modern hall furniture design with sofa set and grey armchairs look chic.\" class=\"wp-image-18768\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/29182056\/hall-furniture-design-with-sofa-set.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/29182056\/hall-furniture-design-with-sofa-set-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/29182056\/hall-furniture-design-with-sofa-set-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/29182056\/hall-furniture-design-with-sofa-set-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>The space enclosed within the book showcase acts as a perfect nook for reading books or enjoying a cup of coffee while soaking in the city view<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Lets plan your home interiors together, speak to designers now\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/28124401\/lets-plan-home-interiors-together.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Hall Furniture Design That Gives Your Guests A Warm Welcome<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This light wooden rack gives a rustic and warm vibe to the entryway space. It is a perfect choice of furniture design for small halls. It has transformed an otherwise dead\/overlooked space into something more lively and elegant. The mirror placed at the vantage point with a green plant completes the overall look and mood of the space.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/29182139\/wooden-rack-home-furniture-design-in-hall.jpg\" alt=\"Light wooden rack home furniture design in the hall brings a rustic and warm vibe to the entryway space.\" class=\"wp-image-18776\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/29182139\/wooden-rack-home-furniture-design-in-hall.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/29182139\/wooden-rack-home-furniture-design-in-hall-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/29182139\/wooden-rack-home-furniture-design-in-hall-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/29182139\/wooden-rack-home-furniture-design-in-hall-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>This wooden rack helps you neatly organise all your bags, shoes and coats and that of your guests too at designated places without overpowering the decor of the room<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Centre Tables That Draw Your Attention<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This is an Asian and Portuguese-style hall furniture design with the complete sofa set and pair of gorgeous centre tables. The white cushion accentuates the look of the seating area while giving it a personal touch with traditional blue decorative plates on the walls. The green plants seamlessly bring nature indoors.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/29182120\/simple-hall-furniture-design-of-centre-table.jpg\" alt=\"Portuguese style simple hall furniture design with sofa set and two centre table is gorgeous.\" class=\"wp-image-18772\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/29182120\/simple-hall-furniture-design-of-centre-table.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/29182120\/simple-hall-furniture-design-of-centre-table-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/29182120\/simple-hall-furniture-design-of-centre-table-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/29182120\/simple-hall-furniture-design-of-centre-table-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>The traditional chest of drawers with intricate handles standing against the wall is the key highlight of this hallway area<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Hall Furniture Design That Creates An Informal Vibe<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This is a simple hall furniture design theme wherein the comfortable recliner brings in a casual and informal vibe into the space while the double glass centre table is an absolute masterpiece. The higher slab is fixed and the lower slab is movable on wheels which gives you extra table space whenever you need it.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/29182114\/recliner-home-furniture-design-for-hall.jpg\" alt=\"Home furniture design for hall, Blue recliner and double glass centre table furniture is an absolute masterpiece.\" class=\"wp-image-18771\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/29182114\/recliner-home-furniture-design-for-hall.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/29182114\/recliner-home-furniture-design-for-hall-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/29182114\/recliner-home-furniture-design-for-hall-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/29182114\/recliner-home-furniture-design-for-hall-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>This blue-and-brown-themed living area looks soothing and pleasant to the eyes<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Showcase For All Things Precious<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Display all that\u2019s precious and close to you in this built-in hall showcase furniture design. The design looks symmetrical and contemporary with multiple equally spaced shelves and classy woodwork.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/29182102\/hall-showcase-furniture-design.jpg\" alt=\"Built-in hall showcase furniture design with multiple equally spaced shelves and elegant woodwork.\" class=\"wp-image-18769\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/29182102\/hall-showcase-furniture-design.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/29182102\/hall-showcase-furniture-design-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/29182102\/hall-showcase-furniture-design-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/29182102\/hall-showcase-furniture-design-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>This hall showcase helps you show off your favourite book collections, travel souvenirs and much more<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">TV Furniture Design In Hall<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Give your TV\/entertainment unit a special place by incorporating it into a TV showcase design that extends from wall to wall. The white cabinets and open shelves give you extra space to store your gaming consoles, equipment, books, smaller items and whatnot. The multi-coloured sofas, glass and wooden centre table and the lighting options are the icings on the cake.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/29182108\/hall-tv-furniture-design.jpg\" alt=\"Hall tv furniture designed with cabinets and open shelves stored with equipment and books looks classic.\" class=\"wp-image-18770\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/29182108\/hall-tv-furniture-design.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/29182108\/hall-tv-furniture-design-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/29182108\/hall-tv-furniture-design-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/29182108\/hall-tv-furniture-design-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>This hall furniture design is a creative blend of domestic charm and modern appeal<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Symmetrical Hall Furniture Design<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This is a modern and minimalistic living room in tones of blue, brown and peach. It features both balance and symmetry in the way the furniture and decor are organised. The wall-mounted shelves help you optimise the space and store all your smaller items.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/29182133\/wall-shelves-furniture-design-for-hall.jpg\" alt=\"Wall furniture design for hall, a minimalist living room in tones of blue, and peach designed with open wall shelves.\" class=\"wp-image-18775\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/29182133\/wall-shelves-furniture-design-for-hall.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/29182133\/wall-shelves-furniture-design-for-hall-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/29182133\/wall-shelves-furniture-design-for-hall-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/29182133\/wall-shelves-furniture-design-for-hall-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>The stick lights hanging from the ceiling and the centre table complement one another<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Get a Free Modular Kitchen Worth \u20b92 Lakhs with Your Home Interiors.\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/08183703\/designcafe-offer-free-modular-kitchen-worth-2-lakhs.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Hall Furniture Design That Lends A Sophisticated Ambience<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This dark grey curved sofa visually demarcates the living room, hallway and the dining room and looks beautiful. The wooden chest of tables contrasts well with the overall design of the room while the lights on the ceiling lend a sophisticated ambience.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/29182126\/sofa-and-dining-table-modern-hall-furniture-design.jpg\" alt=\"Modern hall furniture design, grey curved sofa and a wooden chest of tables bring soothing to the area.\" class=\"wp-image-18773\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/29182126\/sofa-and-dining-table-modern-hall-furniture-design.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/29182126\/sofa-and-dining-table-modern-hall-furniture-design-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/29182126\/sofa-and-dining-table-modern-hall-furniture-design-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/29182126\/sofa-and-dining-table-modern-hall-furniture-design-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Curved pieces of furniture like the sofa and the dining chairs in an open-plan living space help break up the hard angles of architecture<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Hope this blog post has given you enough inspiration to choose the right furniture pieces to complement your hall decor and take it to the next level. Undertake the transformation and let your hall live up to its full potential!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<iframe title=\"Renovate Your Home With Design Cafe\u2019s Modular Furniture | House Renovation Under Budget in 2024\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" src=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/embed\/IclJWCqSJnU?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen><\/iframe>\n<\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Explore, more about<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/multifunctional-furniture-designs\/\">Multifunctional Furniture Designs<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/housekeeping\/how-to-clean-wood-furniture\/\">How To Clean Wood Furniture<\/a><\/li><\/ul>\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"row blog-form\">\n\t<div class=\"offset-lg-3 col-lg-6 bg-light\">\n<fieldset class=\"field-set\">\n<!-- <legend align=\"left\"> 